Cheung Fo / The Mission

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Released 1999, this is a Hong Kong action film in Cantonese with English (and Spanish) subtitles -- keep in mind the sound is an important part of the movie.  Triad boss Lung, who has just escaped being killed in an assassination attempt, hires five bodyguards whose mission is to protect Lung until they can find out who is trying to kill him.  This is a great film if you like interesting characters, a non-transparent plot line and ... well ... guns -- but not cheesy, gratuitous gunfights (okay, the sniper scene is cheesy).

